==Pro Tools Track color coding==

To assign a color to a track open the color palette via

'''Window > Color Palette''' 

When the color palette appears make sure you select '''Track''' as the option to affect.


[[File:Pro Tools color palette with click highlight .png]]




[[File:Pro Tools color palette with track selection menu dropped down.png]]


Then select the track in the edit window and choose the new color from the Color Palette.


